Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:08:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:536605,538732}Nie zginę.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.73,0:09:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:538732,540609}Siostro…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:540609,542402}Isabelle.
